            <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_256gc' title='Col. 256GC &mdash; HL Deb 05 June 2003 vol 648 c256GC' name='column_256gc' href='#column_256gc' rel='bookmark'>256GC</a>
            that might be reached to talk about smaller commercial vessels on a short voyage where the arguments which are applicable to fishing vessels would apply, we could think about that and discuss it between now and Report. However, we would be reluctant to do what the amendments do; that is, to extend the fishing defence much more widely.</p><p>
