            <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_300gc' title='Col. 300GC &mdash; HL Deb 05 June 2003 vol 648 c300GC' name='column_300gc' href='#column_300gc' rel='bookmark'>300GC</a>
            such licences. That is not too much to ask. However, with those comments, I beg leave to withdraw the amendment.
          </p>
