          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S5LV0648P0_20030605_GCR_280' title='Link to this speech by Mr William Bradshaw' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mr-william-bradshaw" title="Mr William Bradshaw">Lord Bradshaw</a></cite>
          <p class='first-para'>
            I do not.
          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S5LV0648P0-06346'>
        <a name='S5LV0648P0_20030605_GCR_281'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-charles-lyell' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S5LV0648P0_20030605_GCR_281' title='Link to this speech by Mr Charles Lyell' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
